{"tid":1981784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔識政治/基本法，但以後係咪可以用「西環治港」做文宣？","createTime":"2020-04-21T00:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T02:14:33.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e77e70b8d63dce0a273f4bd98e52d1bc1a645d78","tid":1981784,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T00:54:06.000Z","msg":"利申唔識 政治/基本法 港豬一名<br />\n<br />\n以往港府一直否認「西環治港」<br />\n隨意Google 一下舊新聞：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180117&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20276646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180117%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20276646&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=2a109fdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180117%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20276646&h=bcd4484c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180117&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20276646</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭強調「並不存在中聯辦干預屬於香港高度自治嘅事務或者施政工作，更加唔存在西環治港嘅說法」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家中聯辦自己衝出嚟話對香港事務有「監督權」可以指指點點，即係「西環治港」啦<br />\n<br />\n以後香港市民有任何意見，應該直接向西環提出，去西環遊行請願而唔係去政總<br />\n<br />\n文宣「西環治港」呢樣，保皇/藍絲 等等應該駁唔到？<br />\n<br />\n講到一舊舊，有無人指教一下🙏"},{"pid":"ef027485396d055c7110a75d37b27ef705e043f3","tid":1981784,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原則上可以"},{"pid":"0dcb3478f2bb54e007df39b9b1b566688d6732f9","tid":1981784,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:04:13.000Z","msg":"用「西環治港」四個字，簡簡單單，方便向港豬做文宣"},{"pid":"5ca635c9ab46c6803963cb5e4da17f94c0b19968","tid":1981784,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:11:12.000Z","msg":"支聯會嘅權力突然膨漲，應該有好多有錢佬都知驚，尤其係支那嚟嗰批"},{"pid":"35bb8e95f080e1412598380aac49e9810b22e8f5","tid":1981784,"uid":37722,"li